3 university of Hawaii and other executive branch departments and
4 a supplemental award for the other executive branch departments
5 related to temporary hazard pay. These amounts are in addition
6 to the amounts provided in Act 29, Session Laws of Hawaii 2025:
7 FY 2025-2026
8 General funds $66,795,019
9 Interdepartmental transfers $306,532
10 Revolving funds $203,736
11 The sums appropriated shall be expended by the appropriate
12 state departments for the purposes of this section:
