6 PART IV
7 SECTION 5. Funds appropriated or authorized by this Act
8 shall be allotted by the director of finance to the appropriate
9 state departments for expenditure in fiscal year 2025-2026 for
10 the purposes of this Act, including the repayment of general
11 fund loans by the general fund appropriations made in this Act,
12 which shall be deemed to be an authorized expenditure under the
13 general fund appropriations made in this Act.
14 SECTION 6. Neither this Act nor the appropriations made in
15 this Act shall be construed as an admission of liability, in any
16 arbitration, administrative proceeding, or court, nor as a
17 legislative determination of the merits of any grievance or
18 related litigation, nor as authority for the legislature to
19 resolve, settle, or adjudicate any grievance or related
20 litigation.
