Report Title:
Public Employment Cost Items; BU-1 and BU-10; Emergency
Appropriations
Description:
Makes emergency appropriations for collective bargaining cost
items for the members of bargaining units (1) and (10) and their
excluded counterparts to resolve issues related to temporary
hazard pay for fiscal year 2025-2026.
The summary description of legislation appearing on this page is for informational purposes only and is
not legislation or evidence of legislative intent.
